\n<\N[5]>\F[62]\FF[93]\AA[F]...What a magnificent view. Haah... If it
weren't for this situation, I would want
to soak in here leisurely...

\n<Sawa>\F[62]\FF[93]\AA[FF]Yes, that sounds nice... Oh, how about a hot
spring trip with everyone next time?♪

\n<\N[5]>\F[62]\FF[93]\AA[F](...But that's after everything is settled. Ah,
I'll go on a hot spring trip!)

\n<\N[5]>\F[62]\FF[93]\AA[F]How about just Sawa going in? She's the one
being made to dress like that... She
shouldn't be punished, right?

\n<\N[5]>\F[62]\FF[93]\AA[F]I'll go and take a look around within my
range, okay? So, I won't be able to
relax and take my time though...

\n<Sawa>\F[62]\FF[93]\AA[FF]...Um, then... I'm sorry, but just for a
little while...
